  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support Foster to plant 4000 trees in Merida!</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Do you think is normal to feel warmer every year? See neighbors flooded by strong tropical storms?  In Merida, my friends, neighbors, and relatives more often experience these problems and deforestation is one of the main causes. Trees regulate temperature, provide shade, cool the air, and filter water into the ground. Trees are urgently needed to remedy this problem!  I ask your help to, with Kanan Kab, produce and plant 4,000 native trees, benefiting neighbors and families of Merida city.</narrative>
  </description>
